let SettingHeader = new Header('SettingHeader','Setting',false,'section','none')
let introPara1 = new Para('introPara1','The World',`In this version of Teyvat created according to your inner desires, <span class='text'>everything is lewder.</span> Sexual activities are integral to the world in more ways than just biological reproduction - it is <span class='text'>the focus around which societies form</span> around, and influence many traditions of the various nations of the world.<br><br><span class='text'>Sex is talked about very positively</span> - it's almost everyone's favourite pastime, and almost everyone can partake well in it.
`,['Setting//TeyvatImage1.jpg','Setting//TeyvatImage2.jpg'],'none')
let introPara2 = new Para('introPara2','Non-Consensual Sex',`Rape and sexual harrassment is looked down upon but <span class='text'>not illegal</span> and is still present, more prevalent against women. Due to society's "sex-positivity" among other factors, rape and sexual harrassment are seen as <span class='text'>inevitable events towards people that don't willingly accept sexual approaches.</span><br><br>
The only effort made to counter rape is the <span class='text'>existence of prostitution as a respected profession</span> in an attempt to take care of people's sexual tendencies without having to resort to rape, which does <span class='text'>reduce its frequency</span>.
`,['Setting//Rape1.jpg','Setting//Rape2.png'],'none')
let introPara3 = new Para('introPara3','Coming-of-age Ceremonies',`Everyone's 18th birthday is a significant event, celebrated especially so due to the fact that they are now able to have sex with most people. However, there is a lenient grace period of 3 years for the consenting age - so an 18 year old can have sex with a 15 year old.<br><br>All nations have a tradition of conducting <span class='text'>'coming-of-age' ceremonies</span>, usually only for women, where sex is had the day people turn 18 with people chosen either by parents, other relatives or themselves. Popular public figures may have these ceremonies conducted publicly, with grand celebrations, lots of food, and of course lots of sex.
`,'Setting//Comingofage1.png','none','left','horizontal')
let introPara4 = new Para('introPara4','Vision Bearers',`<span class='text'>Vision Bearers</span>, along with their elemental capabilities, are granted their dream bodies - <span class='text'>impeccably attractive bodies with high base sexual performance</span>. Thus, they are seen as sexual icons of society.<br><br>Everyone who gets a vision will become the <span class='text'>biggest targets of sexual desire</span>, and so they are taught to be quite free with their bodies so that they can handle that pressure. The <span class='text'>Ascension trials</span> encourage this through their requirements of experience. As a vision bearer clears these trials, they become more experienced in all kinds of sexual activity which helps them handle the sexual pressure they get from society.
`,['Setting//Vision1.jpg','Setting//Vision2.png'],'none')
let introPara5 = new Para('introPara5','High Pregnancy Rate',`Due to this sexual culture and the lack of normalised methods of contraceptives, <span class='text'>pregnancies are extremely high</span>. Pregnancies happen all the time as a <span class='text'>by-product of sex</span>, but are rarely seen as an unwanted burden, instead just the normal way of life for women.<br><br>While childbirth is an incredibly painful ordeal, the normalisation of pregnancies as a by-product has led to a <span class='text'>lack of care for the mother during labour and childbirth</span> in some regions of Teyvat.<br><br>The prevalence of pregnancies means <span class='text'>massive family sizes</span> for the well-off - a couple may raise nearly a dozen children if they wish. Couples that can't afford to raise such families have the option of <span class='text'>putting them up for adoption</span>, which is also incredibly normalised, so there is less stress on the parents to raise them.
`,['Setting//Babies1.png','Setting//Babies2.jpg'],'none')
let introPara6 = new Para('introPara6','Hilichurls and Humans',`Hilichurls, as a <span class='text'>male-only humanoid species, need human females to reproduce</span>. Hilichurls in this world are <span class='text'>much stronger, overpowering even vision bearers</span> if they have a numbers advantage - but they keep their distance as long as their tribes have a good source of reproduction.<br><br>When tribes run out of human females to use for breeding, they roam areas with human activity, looking for women to capture and <span class='text'>enslave as their "nurseries"</span>. These women are then never seen again, thought to have met their end in fulfilling their forced <span class='text'>duty of giving birth to hilichurls</span>. A lot of disappearing incidents for women are pinned to this fact, whether they find evidence or not.
`,['Setting//Hilichurl1.jpg','Setting//Hilichurl2.png'],'none')
let introPara7 = new Para('introPara7','Slimes',`Slimes, on the other hand, are quite a <span class='text'>weak species</span>. As their condensate is used in lots of materials, slimes are reared and farmed and then when their lifespan is done, the slime is harvested.<br><br><span class='text'>Slime reproduction relies on human semen</span>, so as the years went by, slimes have taken forms more appealing to the male mind such as <span class='text'>attractive slime girls</span>. Despite their human appearance, their intelligence is almost non-existent, their instincts only telling them to roam around and have sex with human males.
`,['Setting//Slime1.jpg','Setting//Slime2.png'],'none')
let introPara8 = new Para('introPara8','Fatui',`The Fatui males <span class='text'>give up their reproductive function</span> in exchange for their elemental powers, while Fatui females have their <span class='text'>reproductive function reduced drastically</span>. This has necessitated them to take in non-fatui males to mate with Fatui females.<br><br>Such subjects are <span class='text'>pumped full of drugs to keep their semen flowing</span>, as they will have to fill the wombs of multiple Fatui females multiple times for the <span class='text'>small possibilities of pregnancy</span>. This is extremely taxing on the body and mind.
`,['Setting//Fatui1.jpg','Setting//Fatui2.jpg'],'none')

